Class RadarUserInsightsLocation

  • io.radar.sdk.model.RadarUserInsightsLocation

  • public class RadarUserInsightsLocation

    Represents a learned home or work location. For more information about Insights, see https://radar.io/documentation/insights.

    See Also:

        Represents a learned home or work location. For more information about Insights, see https://radar.io/documentation/insights.

        Parameters:
        type - The type of the learned location.
        location - The learned location.
        confidence - The confidence level of the learned location.
        updatedAt - The datetime when the learned location was updated.
        country - The country of the learned location. May be null.
        state - The state of the learned location. May be null.
        dma - The DMA of the learned location. May be null.
        postalCode - The postal code of the learned location. May be null.

        https://radar.io/documentation/insights
